OL,7,FEmergency accommodation will be
OL,8,Fprovided to people who are rough
OL,9,Fsleeping in Reading during freezing
OL,10,Ftemperatures this week.
OL,12,FThe council has activated its Severe
OL,13,FWeather Emergency Protocol (SWEP)
OL,14,Fwhich will stay in place until next
OL,15,FMonday (25 November).
OL,17,FWhen the temperature drops to zero
OL,18,Fdegrees or below for at least three
OL,19,Fconsecutive nights, the council
OL,20,Fimplements SWEP alongside charity St
OL,21,FMungo's.
