OL,7,FReading Borough Council says forecasts
OL,8,Fand temperatures will be monitored
OL,9,Fthroughout the winter to make sure
OL,10,Fpeople can be kept safe.
OL,12,FMatt Yeo, Lead Councillor for Housing,
OL,13,Fsaid: "Reading is proud of its
OL,14,Fcomprehensive support for the most
OL,15,Fvulnerable in our society.
