OL,7,F"We are acutely aware that those rough
OL,8,Fsleeping on our streets face more
OL,9,Fthreat when the weather turns cold, as
OL,10,Fit has done this week, and I'm pleased
OL,11,Fto see SWEP is now in place to protect
OL,12,Fthem."
OL,14,FThere are a total of 249 bed spaces
OL,15,Foffered across the Council's
OL,16,FHomelessness Support Services to help
OL,17,Fsingle people and couples who are
OL,18,Ffound rough sleeping, or at risk of
OL,19,Frough sleeping. These are in addition
OL,20,Fto those available through the SWEP
OL,21,Fresponse.
