OL,7,FThe council's commitment to tackling
OL,8,Frough sleeping is being strengthened
OL,9,Fby a #121,869 government grant to
OL,10,Fsupport SWEP and the Bed for a Night
OL,11,F(B4N) winter shelter run by FAITH
OL,12,FChristian Group.
OL,14,FThere are also plans to create a
OL,15,Fdaytime warm space between January and
OL,16,FMarch, run by voluntary and charity
OL,17,Fsector partners.
OL,19,FAnybody who sees somebody rough
OL,20,Fsleeping is being urged to report it
OL,21,Fon StreetLink.
